<div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
    <h1 class="mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="lead">
        This Privacy Policy explains how CafeteriaOrderingSystem collects, uses, and protects your personal information when you use our platform.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h4>1. Information We Collect</h4>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Details:</strong> Name, Employee Number, and account credentials</li>
        <li><strong>Order Information:</strong> Menu items selected, restaurant details, total cost, and transaction dates</li>
        <li><strong>System Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, and access times for security logging</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>To process food orders and manage deposits</li>
        <li>To verify user identity for internal company use</li>
        <li>To enhance and maintain the performance of our system</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-4">3. Sharing of Information</h4>
    <p>
        Your information is not shared with third parties outside your organization. It is used solely for internal cafeteria operations.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">4. Security</h4>
    <p>
        We use secure technologies (including HTTPS, database encryption, and access control) to protect your personal data.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">5. Your Rights</h4>
    <p>
        You can request to update, correct, or delete your information by contacting your system administrator.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">6. Changes to This Policy</h4>
    <p>
        This policy may be updated from time to time. Significant changes will be communicated through the system dashboard or email.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">7. Contact Us</h4>
    <p>
        If you have questions about this policy, please contact your internal IT or HR department.
    </p>

    <hr />
    <p class="text-muted">© 2025 CafeteriaOrderingSystem. All rights reserved.</p>
</div>
